G

gatherArray(T, Operand, int[], int[], int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ProcessCommSlave
Takes elements from all processes and gathers them to root process, the data container is array, process i send data interval [sendfroms[i], sendtos[i]) to root process, placed in the same positions, s.t.
gatherArray(T, Operand, int[][], int[][], int, int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ThreadCommSlave
Takes elements from all processes and all threads and gathers them to root process and root thread, the data container is array, process i thread j send data interval [sendfroms[i][j], sendtos[i][j]) to root process and root thread, placed in the same positions, s.t.
gatherArrayProcess(T, Operand, int[], int[], int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ThreadCommSlave
This function call ProcessCommSlave.gatherArray(Object, Operand, int[], int[], int) actually, each process allow only one thread to call this function, just like process communication.
gatherMap(Map<String, T>, Operand, int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ProcessCommSlave
Takes elements from all processes and gathers them to root process, the data container is map, the data in map regardless of the order, if different process have same keys, only one key(random) will be saved in root process.
gatherMap(Map<String, T>, Operand, int, int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ThreadCommSlave
Takes elements from all processes and threads and gathers them to root process and thread, the data container is map, the data in map regardless of the order, if different process and thread have same keys, only one key(random) will be saved in root process and thread.
gatherMapProcess(Map<String, T>, Operand, int) - Method in class com.fenbi.mp4j.comm.ThreadCommSlave
This function call ProcessCommSlave.gatherMap(Map, Operand, int) actually, each process allow only one thread to call this function, just like process communication.
